Rowdy Wolf:





Rowdy Wolf tilted his snout into the air. He could smell Zyber coming. He 
pondered for the reasons she may be reaturning. Just to say good-bye, or 
stay a while longer. He wasn't the one to guess, he wasn't well keen on 
guessing other's actions. Only behaviors. Animals, not bots.

He cocked his head back and howled, giving Zyber his location.
